README

This directory `/data/upload` is to keep the files the users upload.
It should has an owner permission 755 for user apache or www.

    $ ls -l /data/
    ...
    drwxr-xr-x 47 apache root  4096 Jan 28  2021 upload

The files upload from users will be categorized by id of the user.

    $ ls /data/upload/
    100  103  107  110  116  119  122  128	131  134  137  141  145  150  153
    101  104  108  114  117  120  123  129	132  135  139  142  146  151  155
    102  105  109  115  118  121  125  130	133  136  140  144  148  152  157

The directory should be on a separated partition (LVM) or mount on a nfs partition.

